{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/ps_Steam_rough_2023-10-05_v2_test-2_1_1.gif?t=1722833715\" /><br>An unexplored world, with everything you need.<br><br>Survivors of a homeworld devastated beyond hope of restoration, you escaped into deep space, looking for a new planet to call home.<br><br>You discovered an unknown planet rich in resources and unique life forms.<br><br>Explore the planet, gather resources, and fight monsters to ensure your survival!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/en_ps_midashi_1.png?t=1722833715\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/\u30b5\u30cf\u3099\u30a4\u30cf\u3099\u30eb1.gif?t=1722833715\" /><br>A breathtaking world awaits, filled with lush forests, towering mountains, crystal-clear seas, and mysterious ruins. Every corner of the planet holds secrets to uncover, daring you to explore its hidden wonders.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/en_ps_midashi_2.png?t=1722833715\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/\u30b5\u30cf\u3099\u30a4\u30cf\u3099\u30eb2.gif?t=1722833715\" /><br>The planet is home to a variety of unique monsters, some lightning-quick, others airborne. Defeating them gives you materials, while trapping and capturing them allows you to tame them. Tamed monsters can be ridden as mounts, or bred with their own kind to bear offspring. Bringing them into your everyday life will make survival that much easier.<br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/en_ps_midashi_3.png?t=1722833715\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/\u30b5\u30cf\u3099\u30a4\u30cf\u3099\u30eb3.gif?t=1722833715\" /><br>This vast open world of a planet requires you to be self-sufficient in everything, from food to weapons and equipment. You\u2019ll start out with the bare mininum, but as you progress in the game, you\u2019ll be able to craft building materials and combine them to create your own base! Further improve your base with facilities such as crop fields and fish tanks to increase your resources and expand your options.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/en_ps_midashi_4.png?t=1722833715\" /><br>PROJECT SURVIVAL allows you to enjoy multiplayer with more than one person over a network. Join forces to take down powerful monsters, or collaborate to explore the wide, wide world!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/ps_Steam_rough_2023-10-05_v2_\u30d5\u30c3\u30bf\u30fc.png?t=1722833715\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1722833715","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1722833715","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1722833715","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1722833715","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478130/extras/ps_Steam_rough_2023-10-05_v2_test-2_1_1